2. Admin Site Customization — Django
Build a Product Review Backend with DRF — Part 2

In order to use the Django admin first, we need to create superuser using the following command:
    python manage.py createsuperuser

Then enter the following:
    Username (leave blank to use ‘info’): admin
    Email address: admin@gmail.com
    Password: 1234

Runserver and navigate to http://localhost:8000/admin  . You should see login page:
    python manage.py runserver
